{"tid":98009,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳舉辦4天「做愛節」　狂野縱慾大解放","createTime":"2017-01-28T05:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T06:05:04.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf96e210061887401e2b8c6a29b2a764cb367658","tid":98009,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"澳洲雪梨在本月26~29日，舉辨一場「做愛真好節」(Festival of Really Good Sex)，參加者可在會中狂歡縱慾，但主辦人班基(Peter Banki)堅稱這是「研討會」。 <br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，班基強調，這個做愛節主要是一個工作坊，讓參加者探討性愛、金錢與權力，尤其是「有錢能使人做愛」的爭議話題，長期以來一直被視為不能說的秘密，但現在要透過這個做愛節，讓參加者有深入探討。班基說，參加者可以選擇當恩客或是當妓女，他們交易所使用的「錢」，是大富翁遊戲的玩具鈔票。 <br />\n<br />\n班基也再次強調，這個節慶絕非是充滿著做愛的活動，而是一個有深度思考的工作坊，但他拒絕透露舉辦地點。就有參加者宣稱，透過這個做愛節，讓他探索自己對性的妄想和歡樂。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170127/1044793/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170127%2F1044793%2F&d=QbdtIZsqsWgwJ28ExpSMKoscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=a83cb4e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170127/1044793/</a>"},{"pid":"6078f176cc297448624e5472c7f09772bb8019db","tid":98009,"uid":29126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:51:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abddc2d1df4d028261de520fd70c07efaac31e8c","tid":98009,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:55:20.000Z","msg":"愛滋病交流會？"},{"pid":"99d21192bbf0ed340aa91716c63fdca44b3b8223","tid":98009,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"施記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0350637392dc81311095dea9896a4852c445220f","tid":98009,"uid":25676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"施旖婕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}